    "en": {
      "name": "Red-Eyes Black Fullmetal Dragon",
      "effect": "Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned with \"Enhanced Metalmorph\" activated by Tributing a Level 5 or higher Dragon monster. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Red-Eyes Black Fullmetal Dragon\" once per turn. You can reveal this card in your hand; Set 1 \"Metalmorph\" Trap from your Deck, and if you do, shuffle this card into the Deck. When your opponent activates a card or effect (Quick Effect): You can negate the activation, then you can inflict damage to them equal to 1 of their Attack Position monsters' original ATK.",
      "official": false
    },
